
---

## FILE 3: `.gitignore`

```gitignore
# dotcalculation .gitignore

# Temporary files
*.tmp
*.temp
*.log
*.bak
*.old
*.orig

# IDE files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.idea/
.vscode/
.vs/

# Build files
*.exe
*.out
*.app
*.dll
*.so
*.dylib

# Node modules (if any)
node_modules/
package-lock.json

# Environment
.env
.env.local
secrets.h
config.h

# Keep essential files
!index.html
!README.md
!*.html
!*.md
